      "id": "grammar-018-001",
      "english": "Near Future (-kũ-) = later today: Atumia nĩ mekũ-uga mbu (Women will make distress sound), Wee nĩ ũkũ-huha mĩruri (You will whistle). Distant Future (-ka-) = tomorrow/later: Atumia nĩ makã-uga mbu, Wee nĩ ũka-huha mĩruri",
